---
title: Honey Mustard Chicken with Roast Veggie Couscous & Lemon Yoghurt
description: The classic combination of honey and mustard never goes amiss. We love the way these flavours caramelise in the pan. We’ve used chicken thigh here because it packs a fantastic flavour, remains moist as it cooks and complements the bed of
delicious roast veggie couscous.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-mustard-chicken-2fe51c72.jpg
